data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom, 3-bath home nestled in the desirable Port Neches-Groves school district. This spacious residence offers an abundance of features that will make you feel right at home. Inside, the home boasts generously sized rooms throughout, providing ample space for comfortable living. The well-appointed bedrooms offer a tranquil haven for rest and relaxation, while the three bathrooms ensure convenience and privacy for the entire household. The floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and kitchen, making it an ideal space for entertaining guests and creating lasting memories. The kitchen features modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a functional layout. This home offers access to excellent educational opportunities. Additionally, its convenient proximity to local amenities, shopping centers, and parks ensures a convenient and enjoyable lifestyle. This home has NEVER FLOODED! Seller will give help with buy down with right offer.
